; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(101, 101, 101); clear: left; font-family: arial; line-height: 16px; text-align: justify; ">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(101, 101, 101); clear: left; font-family: arial; line-height: 16px; text-align: center; ">\r\n	<span style="font-size: 12px; "><span style="font-family: tahoma, geneva, sans-serif; "><img alt="" src="http://cheapdeal.vn/Uploads/images/laylaimatkhau.gif" style="border: 0px; width: 521px; height: 161px; " /></span></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(101, 101, 101); clear: left; font-family: arial; line-height: 16px; text-align: justify; ">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(101, 101, 101); clear: left; font-family: arial; line-height: 16px; text-align: justify; ">\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:times new roman,times,serif;">Bạn vui l&ograve;ng nhập email đ&atilde; đăng k&iacute; v&agrave; nhấn v&agrave;o n&uacute;t &quot; Đặt lại m&acirc;̣t kh&acirc;̉u&quot;</span></span></span></p>'),
